sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(TLS termination + Auth)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>(local or remote)
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Orchestrator
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, PG: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    Ingress->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP<br/>(auth validated at ingress)
    LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)<br/>TLS configurable (VLLM_TLS_VERIFY)
    vLLM-->>LS: Inference Response
    LS->>PG: INSERT inference log<br/>async (queue: 10000, writers: 4)<br/>Username/password auth
    LS-->>Ingress: JSON Response
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client, Milvus: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/inference/chat_completion<br/>+ RAG context
    Ingress->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>Milvus: Vector similarity search<br/>HTTP/gRPC, Token (MILVUS_TOKEN)
    Milvus-->>LS: Relevant document chunks
    LS->>vLLM: POST embedding request<br/>VLLM_EMBEDDING_URL<br/>Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Embeddings
    LS->>vLLM: POST inference with context<br/>VLLM_URL<br/>Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Augmented response
    LS->>PG: INSERT conversation log<br/>async
    LS-->>Ingress: Augmented JSON Response
    Ingress-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client, K8s: Flow 3: Model Evaluation (TrustyAI LMEval)
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/eval/*
    Ingress->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>K8s: Create LMEval Job<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>LS: Job created
    Note right of K8s: LMEval Job runs<br/>evaluates against vLLM
    LS-->>Ingress: Evaluation initiated
    Ingress-->>Client: Job status

    Note over Client, FMS: Flow 4: Safety Shield Evaluation
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/safety/*
    Ingress->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>FMS: Safety check request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS via FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH
    FMS-->>LS: Safety evaluation result
    LS-->>Ingress: Safety response
    Ingress-->>Client: Response
